 answers to a lot of my questions.  so far i really enjoy the class and can't wait untill i get some of my upper lvl spells.<br><br>i saw icecommet cast the other day while in unrest with my cleric and was stopped dead in my tracks... litterally... divine aura dropped, got stunned and saw it cast infront of me before i died<br><br>i hate being trained<br><br><br>Hutar<br>monk 17 karana<br><br>Fazudno Oom<br>wizard 20 karana<br><br>Doublehutar Hutar<br>warrior 28 karana<br><br>Deekkonn<br>cleric 15 karana<br><br>Neohutar<br>ranger 1 karana<br><br>you say i play too much.  well, i say that it's you who can't get enough of me.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
