	   <tr><td colspan=2>OK first off i hope you have a Staff of Temperate Flux(STF) or something that you can right click instant cast that does dmg or something to aggro the mob. Get SOW or fire up the JBOOTS. Target one mob and click your STF now run, as you find similiar mobs, target and click you STF as you run. Now lets say you have 3 mobs that you pissed off, run in a big circle(change the view of the screen at this point so you can see if they are lumped together). When they are run straight for about 7 secs, stop and cast BOF. Hopefully all 3 get snared, if not run and try to snare the mob by itself then run in big circles and regroup them again. resnare all mobs. now cast your best aoe spell and bang 3 dead mobs. I would try doing this with low lvl mobs to get the hang of it(like skelies)<br><br>Smackin Mobsaround &lt;Merciless Elites&gt;<br>lvl 52 wiz<br>Terris-Thule <br><br>Kill all that opposes the cause...ah f_@k that kill everything!!! <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
